<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Dashboard for {{full_path}}</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="{{path_to_root}}css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="{{path_to_root}}css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                <li class="active"><a href="{{path_to_root}}dashboard.html">Dashboard</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{path_to_root}}index.html">Source</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>
<div class="container">

    <div class="progress tombstones-total">
        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-default" style="width: 100%">
            <strong>{{tombstones_count}} Tombstones</strong>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="progress tombstones-distribution">
        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" style="width: {{dead_percent}}%">
            <strong>{{dead_count}} Dead</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-danger" style="width: {{undead_percent}}%">
            <strong>{{undead_count}} Undead</strong>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <h2>Tombstones in your Code</h2>
    <p class="small">Undead tombstones (&quot;Vampires&quot;) should be removed. Code confirmed to be dead can be removed after a while.</p>
{{tombstones_view}}

    <hr />

    <h2>Deleted Tombstones</h2>
    <p class="small">Those tombstones have been found in the logs, but not in the source code. They're assumed to be deleted.</p>
{{deleted_view}}
</div>
<footer>
    <div class="container">
        <hr/>
        <p><small>Generated by <a href="http://github.com/scheb/tombstone-analyzer" target="_top">scheb/tombstone-analyzer</a> {{version}} at {{date}}.</small></p>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
